@gal/swarm is a provider-neutral burst-compute swarm planning library (capacity
decisions, cost ranking, topology routing, evidence ledgers). It is a pure
planning library — it does not provision resources or import provider SDKs.

This project builds on open work — see CREDITS.md for attributions.
